OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1782319683
OL,3,CJersey sets up free Meningitis B
OL,4,Cvaccine clinic for students
OL,6,FPublic Health Jersey has announced it
OL,7,Fwill open a free walk-in clinic to
OL,8,Fgive students meningitis B
OL,9,Fvaccinations.
OL,11,FThose born between 1 September 2007
OL,12,Fand 31 August 2008 or under 25 and
OL,13,Fstarting further education for the
OL,14,Ffirst time, including university, are
OL,15,Feligible.
OL,17,FThe Government had already announced
OL,18,Fthat it was working on a summer
OL,19,Frollout, following the UK's plan that
OL,20,Fwas unveiled on 12 June.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
