OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1782319683
OL,3,CJersey sets up free Meningitis B
OL,4,Cvaccine clinic for students
OL,6,FIt comes after an outbreak in Kent
OL,7,Fearlier this year, as well as clusters
OL,8,Fof infections in Dorset and Reading.
OL,10,FThe Jersey clinics will take place at
OL,11,Fthe Town Church in St Helier across
OL,12,FJuly and August, with exact dates and
OL,13,Ftimes to be confirmed - including
OL,14,Fevening sessions.
OL,16,FPublic Health Jersey estimates that
OL,17,Fmore than 1,000 people could come
OL,18,Fforward.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/5
