FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1782319683
OL,3,CJersey sets up free Meningitis B
OL,4,Cvaccine clinic for students
OL,6,FThe Meningitis B vaccination requires
OL,7,Ftwo doses, at least 28 days apart, for
OL,8,Ffull protection.
OL,10,FWhilst students will be able to
OL,11,Freceive their second dose in the UK,
OL,12,FPublic Health Jersey is encouraging
OL,13,Fthem to get their first dose in July
OL,14,Fand their second in August, so the
OL,15,Ffull course is completed before they
OL,16,Fstart university.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
