PN,35804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1782319683
OL,3,CJersey sets up free Meningitis B
OL,4,Cvaccine clinic for students
OL,6,FMeningitis is a serious and
OL,7,Fpotentially life-threatening condition
OL,8,Fwhich affects people of all ages,
OL,9,Falthough it is most common in babies,
OL,10,Fchildren, and young adults.
OL,12,FBabies have only been offered the
OL,13,Fvaccine since 2015, which means those
OL,14,Fover the age of 11 are unlikely to be
OL,15,Fprotected.
OL,17,FThose set to start university are
OL,18,Fdeemed more at risk because they are
OL,19,Flikely to be living in shared
OL,20,Faccommodation and mixing with lots of
OL,21,Fdifferent people.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/5
