PN,35805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1782319683
OL,3,CJersey sets up free Meningitis B
OL,4,Cvaccine clinic for students
OL,6,FEmma Baker, Health Protection Senior
OL,7,FNurse Advisor at Public Health Jersey,
OL,8,Fsaid that "this is a targeted offer
OL,9,Ffor the 2026 cohort, and we encourage
OL,10,Fall eligible students to take up the
OL,11,Fvaccine this summer".
OL,13,FIn Guernsey, Alex Hawkins-Drew,
OL,14,FAssociate Director at Public Health,
OL,15,Ftold ITV News on Friday 12 June that
OL,16,Fthey were "aware of the programme
OL,17,Fplanned in the UK and working on a
OL,18,Flocal offer".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/5
